    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies for exceptional throttle response. The dual-VANOS system has been professionally serviced, ensuring precise valve timing across the power band. The chassis is sorted with a reinforced rear subframe and upgraded polyurethane bushings to sharpen handling geometry. Drive is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. While the exterior shows light road use, the mechanical vitals are top-tier, including documented rod bearing replacement and a cooling system overhaul. It is a mechanically sound, driver-focused example ready for the apex.",
