    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2017 Audi Q7 Premium Plus, finished in a timeless Graphite Gray Metallic. This vehicle has been a reliable family companion and shows the pride of ownership throughout. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical for a car of this age. The 20-inch alloy wheels are in excellent shape with only very minor curb rash on the passenger side rear. Inside, the Nougat Brown leather upholstery is supple and free of tears or heavy bolsters wear. All technological features, including the Virtual Cockpit, panoramic sunroof, and the Bose 3D Surround Sound system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the 3.0T V6 engine pulls strongly and the 8-speed Tiptronic transmission shifts seamlessly. I have adhered to a strict maintenance schedule; the most recent service included a fresh oil change, new cabin air filters, and a brake fluid flush. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a solid, honest vehicle that drives as beautifully as it looks. Includes two keys and all original manuals.",
      "price": 33500.0,
